<br>
The Phinny drop is pretty much where we want it. Sorry, but it's supposed to be rare (I do understand the difference between challenging and boring and frustrating, but we really don't want to redo all the epic quests this late in the game). Everyone's epic seems like it's the hardest to get.<br>
